---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="RankWrangler Privacy" description="Learn how RankWrangler handles data across the platform.">
  <main class="mx-auto min-h-screen w-full max-w-3xl px-6 py-24 text-white/80">
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/60 transition hover:text-white">
      <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 19.5 8.25 12l7.5-7.5" /></svg>
      Back to home
    </a>
    <h1 class="mt-8 font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-white">Privacy & Security</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base">
      We are crafting a full privacy policy alongside the RankWrangler platform launch. Until then, here is how we handle data today:
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6">
      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Seller account data</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          API credentials are stored in encrypted secrets within the server workspace. They never touch the marketing site. Access is restricted to the RankWrangler operations team and audited regularly.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Site analytics</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          We run lightweight, cookie-free analytics focused on page performance and anonymous traffic trends. No personal data is collected on this site.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Contact + waitlist</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          Demo requests go straight to hey@rankwrangler.com. We’ll only use your email to coordinate onboarding conversations and will purge it on request.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-white/60">
      Questions or data requests? Email <a href="mailto:hey@rankwrangler.com" class="underline decoration-[#f3a46d] decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-white">hey@rankwrangler.com</a> and we’ll respond within two business days.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
